    "description": "Cracker is a fast-paced 2D arcade game that challenges you to destroy as many falling blocks as you can before you run out of lives. With increasingly faster falling speed, lasting even 5 minutes should be a great challenge.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Three unlockable characters;<br></li><li> Practice mode - start up to level 40;<br></li><li> Short runs, usually lasting around 5 minutes;<br></li><li> 5 seconds powerups, such as X8 score and block slow down;<br></li><li> Progressively faster block falling speed;<br></li><li> Three user interface themes;<br></li><li> High-Score and High-Combo autosaving;<br></li><li> Score Leaderboard.</li></ul>",
